Like I have said from day one, I am not witch hunting and trying to hang Bush for anything he does.  Still, the idea of a preemptive war is a big deal, and when you march in, you damn well better be able to show some evidence.  The problem here has been the lack of evidence for quite some time, or evidence that turned out to be false.  Produce something that shows Iraq was a threat, and our invasion is justified.  <br>
 <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://guildmagic.com/character.cfm?ID=316564" target="top">Tib</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
