I am aware of this, and this is why I don't put much stock in the disdain France displayed to the American invasion.  Still, you don't know what French representatives would have decided if America had waited their requested 6 months before their invasion.  This isn't a clubhouse meeting, this is the fucking United Nations.  If you say &quot;we will allow you after 6 months&quot;, you had damn well better follow through.  France being France, however, I wouldn’t expect military power from them, but it isn't like America couldn't handle this single handed anyway.<br>
Of course, then didn't say &quot;allow&quot; they said we will be &quot;with you&quot; if you give the inspectors another 6 months.  Germany only wanted a month.<br>
